Name: "Starlight"
Desc: A Blake Bloom that symbolizes the supreme authority of the Black Shores, donned by the leader of the organization.
Bg: She has seen all the stars, journeying to the end of time and space and back. This gleaming star kept her company, a speck of blooming stardust illuminating the night sky and guiding her way home. Listen closely to hear echoes of her prescence.
